Megatron does not change his expression on his face, it is still serious,
and deadly. But inside his mind he is very suprised, and even happy. He
recognized Astrotrain (Astroblast) and Speedbreaker. What were they doing
here? "No" he says turning to Autofire. "Let us land, I need to see them
one on one".
